x-sap-shortText: API to access personal information for an employee.

info.title: Personal Information
info.description:
You can use these APIs to access the personal information of an employee including emergency contact information, social media accounts, email address, and non-effective-dated biographical information such as date of birth, country of birth and national identification card information.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)
